{"word":"G3909 - παρατυγχάνω - paratynchánō - par-at-oong-khan'-o - Meet with","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παρατυγχάνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">paratynchánō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-at-oong-khan'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Meet with</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - எதிர்ப்படு"},{"paragraph":"to chance to be by"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G5177 - τυγχάνω - tynchánō - toong-khan'-o/5177\">G5177</a>; to <i>chance near</i>, that is, <i>fall in with:</i> - meet with.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}